The Feed the Future Innovation Exchange is a database of innovations developed to meet the global challenges of producing more food in a sustainable manner. This tool serves as an online platform for researchers, development organizations, private sector entities, policymakers and donors to foster critical partnerships, identify cutting-edge technologies and practices that meet strategic priorities, locate evidence-based approaches to enhance policy and discover innovations that are ripe for commercialization. How development organizations, private sector entities, policymakers and donors can use the Feed the Future Innovation Exchange:
Achieve wider impact and inform policy with the latest innovations How researchers can use the Feed the Future Innovation Exchange:
Garner partnerships and technology transfer opportunities to scale your innovations